#Bassmaster #BASSElite #StLawrenceRiver

node.text:
This week’s @marathonpetroleum Peak Performance goes to the newest Elite Series champion @takumiitou4663! He came into the final day in 7th place and brought in the biggest five-fish limit of the week to take home the win!
#Bassmaster #BASSElite #StLawrenceRiver

node.text:
A little Sunday magic indeed! @dmullinsfishing is off to a good start on Championship Sunday! Watch all of the action from the @wearefarmers Bassmaster Elite at St. Lawrence River on @fs1 and Bassmaster.com!
#Bassmaster #BASSElite #StLawrenceRiver

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bassmaster on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 5 people and text.

node.text:
It’s the season finale of the 2021 Bassmaster Elite Series and the Top 10 anglers are the last ones standing on the St. Lawrence River. Catch all the action on @foxsports and @fs1 from 8-12:30 ET and Bassmaster.com all day for #basslive @wearefarmers 

1. @coryjohnston_fishing (68-10)
2. @justinatkinsfishing (67-14)
3. @johnston_cj (65-11)
4. @clarkwendlandt (65-9)
5. Bernie Schultz (64-13)
6. @brandonpalaniuk (64-7)
7. @takumiitou4663 (64-0)
8. @dmullinsfishing (62-2)
9. @austinfelixfishing (61-4)
10. @chrisgrohfishing (60-13)
